          </summary>
          <div class="px-8 pb-6 pt-2 bg-blue-950/10">
            <div class="text-gray-200 leading-relaxed">
              SOC 2 refers to SOC 2 Type II certification, a recognized security compliance standard. Capgo is SOC 2 Type II certified, meaning its systems and processes are independently audited to ensure high standards of security, availability, and confidentiality, including data protection, access controls, service reliability, and safe data handling. In practice, this means Capgo follows enterprise-grade security practices and can be used by companies with compliance requirements, corporate clients, and B2B or regulated environments. SOC 2 included in the Enterprise tier.
            </div>
          </div>
        </details>

